The show is more recommended for batman fans. It his worth becoming a batman fan just to watch it. Amazing show,great acting,gripping,and one hundred percent a must see. The show hold you on,and on the edge of your seat for all 22 episodes of season 1. The way it plays out is incredible. They have three young actors at age 12 that are amazing actors. All actors and actresses are shown so incredibly it will keep you up at night wondering what will happen in the next episode. If you like edgy TV series you are in the right place. Ten stars minimum. The show has you wishing you could live the adventures they go through. Although a bit scary we see action,adventures,some romance,and all you would ever want to see.